posts.description: A Psychoanalyst Explains Why Men Draw Dicks on Everything | Broadly
posts.extended: As a woman, I can't quite classify my relationship to the penis, drawn. On a subconscious level, the scrawled outline of a phallus is instinctively as amusing to me as it is a symbol of threateningly unchecked masculinity.
